[*] --> Rejected
Rejected --> Created : update
Rejected : entry / log transfer
Created --> Reviewed : confirm
Reviewed --> Delivered : cancel
Delivered --> Archived : cancel
Delivered : entry / log transfer
Archived --> Shipped : review
Shipped --> [*]
@enduml